section.section:
Of the 24 Advisory Council members:
Except as provided in paragraph (4) of this subsection, 1 member shall be appointed from a list of qualified individuals submitted to the Governor by each of the following organizations:
The American Heart Association - Mid-Atlantic, Inc.;
The Department;
The Johns Hopkins Medical Institutions;
The Maryland Association of County Health Officers;
The Maryland Hospital Association, Inc.;
The Maryland Nurses Association;
The Medical and Chirurgical Faculty of the State of Maryland;
The Monumental City Medical Society;
The Baltimore Alliance for the Prevention and Control of Hypertension and Diabetes;
The University of Maryland Hospital and School of Medicine;
The Maryland Academy of Family Physicians;
The American College of Emergency Physicians Maryland Chapter;
The American Stroke Association;
The American Society of Internal Medicine;
The Maryland Institute for Emergency Medical Services Systems;
The Maryland State Council on Physical Fitness;
The Maryland Chapter of the American College of Cardiology; and
The Maryland Pharmacy Association; and
Six shall be members of the general public.
